# ngs

> Scripting language created specifically for Ops.
> More information: <https://github.com/ngs-lang/ngs>.

- Execute a code snippet:

`ngs -e "{{echo('ngs is executed')}}"`

- Execute a script:

`ngs {{path/to/script.ngs}}`

- Display version:

`ngs --version`
